&lt;이제… 슬슬 목적지를 이야기 해주고 다니면 좋을 것 같은데.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Don’t you think… it’s about time he started telling us where we’re going?&gt;

KR:
&lt;잠깐, 최종 목적지라는 건…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Wait, so by our final destination, you mean…&gt;

KR:
&lt;이스마엘… 괜찮아?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Ishmael… you good?&gt;
